        <p style="color: rgba(250,250,247,0.78);">No application. No credit pull. A 20-minute conversation where we look at each entity&rsquo;s 1120-S and K-1s if you run satellite offices, your hospital W-2 alongside your S-corp K-1 if you&rsquo;re hospital-affiliated, your IDR servicer statement if you carry residency loans, your 1099-NEC consulting arrangements if applicable, any pending SBA expansion you&rsquo;re considering, and your accumulated multi-entity reserves &mdash; then we tell you which loan program fits and roughly what the numbers look like. If we&rsquo;re not the right shop, we&rsquo;ll tell you that too.</p>
        <div class="final-cta-actions">
          <a href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/schedule-call" class="btn btn-on-dark-primary btn-large">Talk to Our Team</a>
